      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RITZA DUANE (2) is a well performed dog who recorded his 15th career win last time out at this track (22.02). Hard to go past form here at this journey. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Has put together a string of wins and expected to go close again. STAN'S DREAM (8) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 5 lengths at this track in a handy 21.73 beating BRAVE EMBER. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Hard to fault his form and he makes plenty of appeal. NORA'S BOY (1) has a strong overall record having 29 wins and 60 places from 133 starts but was out of the money last time when fourth (22.29) over 383m at this track. Solid record at the distance winning 19 races. Super consistent and can feature with the right run. BRAVE EMBER (7) ran good time (22.06) when second last start over 383m at this track, the second placing in a row.",
